WEBVTT

00:29.376 --> 00:31.459
(newsreel music)

00:34.209 --> 00:36.917
<i>Sparkling diamonds,
their value running into millions,</i>

00:37.042 --> 00:39.334
<i>are giving Hatton Garden sleepless nights.</i>

00:39.626 --> 00:41.626
<i>With London
now a world centre for diamonds,</i>

00:41.751 --> 00:43.959
<i>jewel bandits
have made this city thoroughfare</i>

00:44.084 --> 00:45.209
<i>their favourite target.</i>

00:45.334 --> 00:47.376
<i>There have been widespread thefts
of precious stones</i>

00:47.501 --> 00:49.209
<i>worth hundreds of thousands.</i>

00:49.751 --> 00:51.334
<i>To foil the thieves,
Hatton Garden</i>

00:51.459 --> 00:53.251
<i>now has its own giant strong room,</i>

00:53.376 --> 00:56.042
<i>available to every jewel merchant
in the district.</i>

